org.md2k.phonesensor.phone.sensors

Class PhoneSensorDataSource

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.md2k.phonesensor.phone.sensors.PhoneSensorDataSource
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Accelerometer, AmbientLight, AmbientTemperature, Battery, Compass, CPU, Gyroscope, Memory, Pressure, Proximity, StepCount, TouchScreen

    public abstract class PhoneSensorDataSource
extends java.lang.Object
    This class handles the creation of PhoneSensorDataSource objects.

    Each sensor makes one of these objects so it can interact with dataKitAPI. The data sources that inherit from this superclass are:

    • Accelerometer
    • ActivityType
    • AmbientLight
    • AmbientTemperature
    • Battery
    • Compass
    • CPU
    • GeoFence
    • Gyroscope
    • LocationFused
    • Memory
    • Pressure
    • Proximity
    • StepCount
    • TouchScreen
